Italy is financing a $3 million
project aimed at improving  food security  and nutrition for women
and young people in Egypt, the United Nationsâ€™ Food and
Agriculture Organization said.  The program will help teach skills including growing crops,
raising small animals, selling food products and making organic
fertilizer, the Rome-based FAO said today in a  statement  on its
website. The project also will promote nutrition education, the
